name: Saretha von Beel
content: Saretha von Beel was a female human hyperspace prospector active during the High Republic Era. Operating out of Black Spire Outpost on Batuu, von Beel met Jedi Master Lee Harro after being captured by pirates. Harro freed her and returned her to her starship, after which she gave him a lift to the planet Vexos as a favour. After her adventure there, von Beel recounted the events to several patrons of the Enlightenment tapbar on Jedha. She was tall and muscular with dark brown skin and blonde hair, and spoke in a thick accent unfamiliar to Keth Cerepath.
